EN: The rice cooker can make multiple servings of rice at once.
ZH: 我的电饭锅有一个保温功能，可以让米饭保持热久一点。
EN: My rice cooker has a keep-warm function that can keep the rice hot for longer.
ZH: 这款电饭锅有一个快速煮饭的模式，可以在很短的时间内煮熟米饭。
EN: This rice cooker has a quick-cook mode that can cook rice in a short amount of time.
ZH: 我最喜欢的电饭锅是日本品牌的，做出的米饭特别松软。
EN: My favorite rice cooker is a Japanese brand that makes rice particularly fluffy.
ZH: 我的电饭锅上面有数字显示屏，可以很方便地调整煮饭的时间和温度。
EN: My rice cooker has a digital display screen that makes it easy to adjust cooking time and temperature.
ZH: 我的妈妈每天都会用电饭锅来做饭，因为它方便又省事。
EN: My mom uses the rice cooker every day to cook because it's convenient and saves time.
ZH: 这款电饭锅有一个多功能的设置，可以做出不同口味的米饭。
EN: This rice cooker has a multi-function setting that can make different flavors of rice.
ZH: 我的电饭锅是铝制的，做出的米饭更加均匀细腻。
EN: My rice cooker is made of aluminum, which produces more even and delicate rice.
ZH: 我的电饭锅内胆是不粘涂层的，清洗起来很方便。
EN: The inner pot of my rice cooker has a non-stick coating, making it easy to clean.
ZH: 我用电饭锅还可以做煮粥、蒸馒头等菜。
EN: I use the rice cooker to make congee, steam buns, and other dishes.
ZH: 这款电饭锅有一个预约煮饭的功能，可以在你下班前提前设置。
EN: This rice cooker has a schedule cooking function that allows you to set it up before you get off work.
ZH: 我的室友常常忘记关电饭锅，导致米饭被煮干了。
EN: My roommate often forgets to turn off the rice cooker, resulting in dried out rice.
ZH: 我的电饭锅还带有煮粥功能，可以做出浓稠可口的粥。
EN: My rice cooker also has a porridge-making function that can make rich and tasty porridge.
